latestPosts.caption:
Not Sponsored🙏🏼

Highly Recommended 

Name: Mamaearth Rice Facial Kit With Rice Water & Niacinamide 

Price 399/- but mostly on discount on amazon
Back to short hair girl era💇🏻‍♀️🥰

How we planned our trip:

First we went to delhi then took train to sujangarh (3rd AC) reached sujangarh by 5am

Booked 7 seater private cab to khatushyam then salasar balaji and then drop off at sujangarh railway station 4500/-

Sujangarh to new delhi railway station (2nd AC) we reached delhi by 10pm

Completed the trip within 23 hours

Next day took flight to shirdi 

Booked room there! Hotel nam Dwarka park 2500/- for a night

Next day early morning aarti pass 600/- each! 

Then went to sai heritage village
Ticket price 150/- not worth it as maintenance of the village was bad and insights of the village was written in marathi only!

Note: we booked private cab in shirdi too which costed 8000/- but not worth it they scammed us as the regular cab will cost less than 1,000/-

Approximately costed us 35k excluding flight and train tickets! 

Delhi to shirdi flight: approximately 15k

Hope it helps 

Om sai ram🙏🏼
Chasing sunsets and dreams together🍻🧿
